snippet.title: One Night Stand - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The full version of One Night Stand is out now! Available on PC, Mac and Linux.


Download game on:
Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/549860
itch.io - https://kinmoku.itch.io/one-night-stand
Humble - https://www.humblebundle.com/store/one-night-stand

More information and press-kit available at: http://www.gamesbykinmoku.com/one-night-stand
